HOMEFIELD ENERGY  Trademark Information
 ILLINOIS POWER RESOURCES, LLC
Energy management services, namely, providing a service that allows customers to purchase energy, namely, electricity and renewable energy, at a fixed price; Retail electricity provider services that allow customers to purchase electricity and renewable energy




