This is a brand page for the HOMEFIELD ENERGY trademark by ILLINOIS POWER RESOURCES, LLC 
                                in HOUSTON, TX, 77002.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this HOMEFIELD ENERGY trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner ILLINOIS POWER RESOURCES, LLC of the HOMEFIELD ENERGY trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the HOMEFIELD ENERGY trademark.
                           






On Friday, February 17, 2012,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        HOMEFIELD ENERGY by 
                        ILLINOIS POWER RESOURCES, LLC, HOUSTON, TX  77002.
                        The USPTO has given the HOMEFIELD ENERGY 
                        trademark serial  number of  85546145.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for HOMEFIELD ENERGY is 
                        
                        
                                            Mark Tidwell of 
                                            Haynes and Boone, LLP,  2323 Victory Avenue, Suite 700, Dallas TX 75219 
                                .
                            The HOMEFIELD ENERGY trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Advertising,  Business & Retail Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for HOMEFIELD ENERGY 
                            is Energy management services, namely, providing a service that allows customers to purchase energy, namely, electricity and renewable energy, at a fixed price; Retail electricity provider services that allow customers to purchase electricity and renewable energy. 
                            





