Illinois Power Resources Generating, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 1:51 AM ET
Electric Utilities

Company Overview of Illinois Power Resources Generating, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Illinois Power Resources Generating, LLC operates electricity generation facilities. It uses conventional steam coal technology for power generation. The company was formerly known as New AERG, LLC. The company is based in Houston, Texas. Illinois Power Resources Generating, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Illinois Power Holdings, LLC.


601 Travis StreetSuite 1400Houston, TX 77002United States



Phone: 713-507-6400








