Grand Bahama Power Co. Ltd.


                  Grand Bahama Power Co. Ltd., a subsidiary of Emera, Inc., is a company headquartered in Grand Bahama, Bahamas, that supplies electrical power. Sarah R. MacDonald is the CEO, in this role since 2011. On 02 Dec 10 Emera, Inc. acquired Grand Bahama Power Co. Ltd. from MaruEnergy Grand Bahama Ltd. for $82 million.                




